{"tid":196993,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂（有片）- 一雞兩吃（下集） 唐揚炸雞","createTime":"2017-04-11T15:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T14:54:27.000Z","uid":30742,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"469b0a3fa8b79c44ef7e7c924aa91f7e75b9d95b","tid":196993,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zx1Qa0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZx1Qa0J.jpg&h=de800301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bR1XL7gVHd8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbR1XL7gVHd8&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=cdd988cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bR1XL7gVHd8</a><br />\n<br />\n上集提到因為要做豆乳雞湯，只用左雞骨同埋兩片雞胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有翼、鎚同雞脾肉，我又想做番日式料理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最簡單就係就唐揚炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一來唔難啦！二來因為要切塊炸，翼、鎚既肉都可以用埋！<br />\n完全唔會嘥野！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唐揚炸雞  圖文食譜: <br />\n<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/04/karaage-chicken.html \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F04%2Fkaraage-chicken.html%20&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6737834e\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/2017/04/karaage-chicken.html </a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=89dc3f24\" target=\"_blank\"